title: Zeit Eyes 10/27: #TrumpLostOurJobs, The Moon, Saved By The Bell, COVID, Blake Shelton
itunes:title: Zeit Eyes 10/27: #TrumpLostOurJobs, The Moon, Saved By The Bell, COVID, Blake Shelton
description:
On this edition of Zeit Eyes Jack and Miles discuss people who lost their jobs turning on Trump, there is water on the Moon apparently, the trailer for the Saved by the Bell reboot is out, we learn more about the long term effects of COVID every day, and Blake Shelton and Gwen Stefani got engaged...again!
